# LogClarityGrid - Log Pattern Visualizer

LogClarityGrid extracts the top patterns and burst zones from system or application logs using frequency mapping.

## Features
- Pattern summary  
- Burst detection  
- CLI output with filters  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_LogClarityGrid.git
cd 26_LogClarityGrid
python analyze.py logs/app.log
